layout_mode = 2
size_flags_vertical = 3
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "Thanks for downloading my game!
Before you get started, I must warn you that this game is [i]meant[/i] to be played in a language you do not understand. Once you close this popup, the entirety of the game will be in Jeyung, a constructed language I designed. Obviously, I do not expect you to intuit this language, which is why I recommand you visit [url=https://liturgic-compulsions.neocities.org/jeyung-grammar/jeyung-accueil]my website[/url] where you will find a comprehensive grammar as well as a dictionnary that will help you parse this game.
If you wish to play in English or French, though I recommand against it, you can easily edit your save file at your game install location and set the locale to fr or en, if you want to play it in french or english.
With that being said, I bid you a good gaming!
[right]Kyih.[/right]"

